---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { INFO } from "../data/info";
---

<MainLayout title={`Nosotros | ${INFO.name}`}>
  <section class="bg-primary text-base py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <span
        class="text-accent uppercase tracking-widest text-sm font-semibold mb-4 block"
        >Nuestra Historia</span
      >
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-playfair mb-8">
        {INFO.story.title}
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert mx-auto text-white/90">
        <p class="mb-6 indent-8 text-justify">
          {INFO.story.text.split(". ")[0]}.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6 indent-8 text-justify">
          {INFO.story.text.split(". ").slice(1).join(". ")}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="mt-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-left">
        <div
          class="space-y-12 relative before:absolute before:inset-0 before:ml-5 before:-translate-x-px md:before:mx-auto md:before:translate-x-0 before:h-full before:w-0.5 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-transparent before:via-accent before:to-transparent"
        >
          <!-- Item 1: 1995 -->
          <div
            class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group"
          >
            <div
              class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white bg-primary text-accent shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-xs">1995</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)] p-4 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/5 shadow hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 mb-1">
                <div class="font-bold text-white font-playfair text-lg">
                  Fundación
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">
                Nace Taberna Aliaga como un pequeño local familiar. La esencia
                de la cocina tradicional empieza aquí.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 2: 2012 -->
          <div
            class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group"
          >
            <div
              class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white bg-primary text-accent shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-xs">2012</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)] p-4 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/5 shadow hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 mb-1">
                <div class="font-bold text-white font-playfair text-lg">
                  El relevo
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">
                Raúl Aliaga toma el liderazgo. Se introduce el concepto de
                "producto de lonja premium" sin perder la cercanía.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Item 3: Hoy -->
          <div
            class="relative flex items-center justify-between md:justify-normal md:odd:flex-row-reverse group"
          >
            <div
              class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white bg-accent text-primary font-bold shadow shrink-0 md:order-1 md:group-odd:-translate-x-1/2 md:group-even:translate-x-1/2 z-10"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-xs">Hoy</span>
            </div>
            <div
              class="w-[calc(100%-4rem)] md:w-[calc(50%-2.5rem)] p-4 rounded border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 shadow hover:bg-accent/20 transition-colors"
            >
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between space-x-2 mb-1">
                <div class="font-bold text-accent font-playfair text-lg">
                  Resiliencia
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">
                Tras la DANA, resurgimos con más fuerza. Un espacio renovado
                donde la comunidad de Catarroja es familia.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 relative">
        <div
          class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent/20 blur-xl rounded-full opacity-50"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="relative bg-white/5 p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-playfair text-white mb-2">
            Resiliencia y Comunidad
          </h3>
          <p class="italic text-white/80">
            "Nuestro vínculo con Catarroja es inquebrantable. Tras la DANA,
            resurgimos con más fuerza gracias a vosotros."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
